Document: CharFXTransform
Path: godot/classes/class_charfxtransform.rst
Summary: Defines visual transformation properties for character effects.

Inherits: RefCounted

This class holds visual transformation properties for character effects, such as position, rotation, scale, and skew. It's used to define how a character or text element should be visually altered.
