Document: CharFXTransform
Path: godot/classes/class_charfxtransform.rst
Summary: Defines how a single character is rendered within a RichTextEffect.

CharFXTransform
Inherits: RefCounted < Object

Controls how an individual character will be displayed in a RichTextEffect.
---CHUNK---
Document: CharFXTransform
Path: godot/classes/class_charfxtransform.rst
Summary: Defines properties to control the visual transformation of individual characters within a RichTextEffect.

This object allows control over how individual characters are displayed within a RichTextEffect by setting various properties.
---CHUNK---
Document: Class CharFXTransform
Path: godot/classes/class_charfxtransform.rst
Summary: This document describes the CharFXTransform class, which is used for applying visual effects to text characters.

CharFXTransform is a class used to apply visual transformations to individual characters within a RichTextLabel. It allows for effects like scaling, rotation, and color changes on a per-character basis, enabling advanced text animations and styling.

Inherits: Object

